Multi-Author Project Notice and License

This repository originated as a three-person group project (`320-fa24-final-task`)
submitted for CSCI 310, Introduction to Operating Systems, Fall 2024. It was
authored jointly by three contributors:

  - Ben Tran (GitHub: windwalker46)
  - Justin Halvorson (GitHub: Justin-HAL)
  - Daniel Leone (GitHub: dagron27)

This repository is hosted here by Daniel Leone as a personal portfolio copy of
that group project, including a later, individually-authored security
remediation and documentation pass (see README.md's Known Issues / Security
Findings and Contributions sections) performed solely by Daniel Leone.

IMPORTANT SCOPE OF THIS LICENSE:

The MIT License terms below apply ONLY to the portions of this Software
authored by Daniel Leone -- namely his contributions to the original
